results.name: Number of diagonally symmetric polyominoes with n cells.
comment: This sequence counts polyominoes with exactly the symmetry group of order 2 generated by a single reflection about a diagonal.
reference: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
